-----
doing sth for updating node labels on live-migrate?!!!


```
apiVersion: node-labels.openshift.io/v1beta1
kind: OwnedLabels
metadata:
  name: edge-role
spec:
  domain: node-role.kubernetes.io
  namePattern: edge
---
apiVersion: node-labels.openshift.io/v1beta1
kind: Labels
metadata:
  name: edge-role
spec:
  nodeNamePatterns:
    - okd4-edge-edge-.+
  labels:
    node-role.kubernetes.io/edge: ""
```
